imply as '''Laurindo''', is a Portuguese professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]].\n\n==External links==\n*{{ForaDeJogo|name=Laurindo}}\n*{{Soccerway|laurindo-antonio-leal-tavares/112686|Laurindo}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Laurindo Tavares}}\n[[Category:1982 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Portuguese people of Cape Verdean descent]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Lisbon]]\n[[Category:Portuguese footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:LigaPro players]]\n[[Category:Portuguese Second Division players]]\n[[Category:Cypriot Second Division players]]\n[[Category:Real S.C. players]]\n[[Category:Odivelas F.C. players]]\n[[Category:C.D. Olivais e Moscavide players]]\n[[Category:C.D. Pinhalnovense players]]\n[[Category:Atl\u00e9tico Clube de Portugal players]]\n[[Category:F.C. Arouca players]]\n[[Category:U.D. Oliveirense players]]\n[[Category:C.D. Mafra players]]\n[[Category:Clube Oriental de Lisboa players]]\n[[Category:Olympiakos Nicosia players]]\n[[Category:Portuguese expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Cyprus]]\n[[Category:Portuguese expatriate sportspeople in Cyprus]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Portuguese footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Laurindo\n| image = \n| fullname = Laurindo Ant\u00f3nio Leal Tavares \n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1982|6|15|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Lisbon]], [[Portugal]] \n| height = {{height|m=1.73}}\n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n| currentclub =\n| clubnumber = \n| youthyears1 = 1997\u20131998 | youthclubs1 = Oper\u00e1rio Lisboa\n| youthyears2 = 1998\u20132001 | youthclubs2 = [[C.F. Estrela da Amadora|Estrela Amadora]]\n| years1 = 2001\u20132003 | clubs1 = [[Real S.C.|Real Massam\u00e1]] | caps1 = 57 | goals1 = 5\n| years2 = 2003\u20132004 | clubs2 = [[Estrela de Vendas Novas|Estrela Vendas Novas]] | caps2 = 36 | goals2 = 3\n| years3 = 2004\u20132006 | clubs3 = [[Odivelas F.C.|Odivelas]] | caps3 = 49 | 